title: Ep - 127 - TYLER BALTIERRA FROM TEEN MOM OG
description:
Tyler Baltierra from MTV’s Teen Mom OG discusses Catelynn’s pregnancy, how he coped with her miscarriage, his mental health journey, and his thoughts on Bristol Palin joining the show. 


Patrick Hinds, co-host of True Crime Obsessed podcast, reviews Flipping Out on Bravo. 


SiriusXM Radio Producer Alyssa Heimrich reviews this week’s episode of Real Housewives of Orange County on Bravo.
